er options in every manage album page.</li>\n<li>Date info: show 3 kinds of date format (read installation info)</li>\n</ul>";s:17:"short_description";s:112:"This plugin will let you sort the galleries by date and get info about gallery creation (and modification) date.";}i:10;O:8:"stdClass":14:{s:4:"name";s:27:"Effects for NextGEN Gallery";s:4:"slug";s:27:"effects-for-nextgen-gallery";s:7:"version";s:3:"0.9";s:6:"author";s:48:"<a href="http://www.fanninger.at">fanningert</a>";s:14:"author_profile";s:54:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/profile/fanningert";s:12:"contributors";a:1:{s:10:"fanningert";s:54:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/profile/fanningert";}s:8:"requires";s:5:"2.9.2";s:6:"tested";s:5:"3.0.5";s:13:"compatibility";a:1:{s:5:"3.2.1";a:1:{s:3:"0.9";a:3:{i:0;i:100;i:1;i:2;i:2;i:2;}}}s:6:"rating";d:57.19999999999999573674358543939888477325439453125;s:11:"num_ratings";i:14;s:8:"homepage";s:62:"http://www.fanninger.at/page/wp-plugin-effects-nextgen-gallery";s:11:"description";s:968:"<p>Advanced wordpress and NextGen Gallery with some extra effects.\nI only tested the 3.x version without network feature.</p>\n\n<h4>What is EFNGG / What can you expect?</h4>\n\n<ul>\n<li>A non invasive WordPress-plugin that extend NextGen Gallery with some new effects</li>\n<li>Highslide and Lightbox support</li>\n<li>Configuration of the effects over a web option page</li>\n<li>Full i18n-Support through gnutext mo/po files</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Important Links:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/effects-for-nextgen-gallery/changelog/" title="Effects for NextGEN Gallery Changelog">Changelog</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://wordpress.org/tags/effects-for-nextgen-gallery?forum_id=10" title="Wordpress Support Forum">Support Forum</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>TODO</h4>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Add more translation</li>\n<li>Test mit vorherigen Versionen (NextGEN Gallery and Wordpress)</li>\n<li>Download-Option (Highslide) in the Option-Page (no manuell download more)</li>\n